'''Mamoun Darkazanli''' ([[Arabic language|Arabic]]: مأمون داركازنلي (born August 4, 1958) in [[Aleppo]], [[Syria]]) is a citizen of [[Germany]] and [[Syria]] who is wanted in [[Spain]] on terrorism charges.<ref name=refInterpol>[http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20080319222238/http://www.interpol.int/public/Data/Wanted/Notices/Data/2003/83/2003_41083.asp Interpol red notice on Darkazanli]</ref>
He was arrested on October 15, 2004<ref name=refBBC>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3747968.stm |title=BBC reports arrest |publisher=BBC News |date=2004-10-15 |accessdate=2012-03-16}}</ref> in [[Hamburg]] on a Spanish warrant, but freed on July 18, 2005<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4692375.stm |title=BBC reports release |publisher=BBC News |date=2005-07-18 |accessdate=2012-03-16}}</ref> after a ruling by the [[Federal Constitutional Court of Germany]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bundesverfassungsgericht.de/entscheidungen/rs20050718_2bvr223604.html |title=Judgment in German |publisher=Bundesverfassungsgericht.de |date=2005-07-18 |accessdate=2012-03-16}}</ref> Darkazanli is under sanction, as affiliate or supporter of [[al-Qaida]], by the United Nations,<ref name=refUN>{{cite web|url=https://www.un.org/Docs/sc/committees/1267/tablelist.htm |title=UN 1267 Committee banned entity list |publisher=Un.org |date= |accessdate=2012-03-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060728143814/http://www.un.org/Docs/sc/committees/1267/tablelist.htm |archivedate=2006-07-28 |df= }}</ref> by the European Union,<ref name=refEU>{{cite web|url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=CELEX:32002R0881:EN:HTML |title=EU notice |publisher=Eur-lex.europa.eu |date= |accessdate=2012-03-16}}</ref> and by the United States Treasury<ref name=refUS>{{cite web|url=http://www.ustreas.gov/offices/enforcement/ofac/sdn/sdnlist.txt |title=US Treasury SDN and SDGT list |date= |accessdate=2012-03-16}}</ref> as a [[Specially Designated Global Terrorist]]. His company, called Mamoun Darkazanli Import-Export Company or Darkazanli Export-Import Sonderposten, in Hamburg, until recently was listed as well.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.un.org/News/Press/docs/2010/sc9983.doc.htm |title=Delisting of Mamoun Darkazanli Import-Export Company or Darkazanli Export-Import Sonderposten |publisher=Un.org |date= |accessdate=2012-03-16}}</ref>
